<doc id="857583" wikidata="Q2317254" url="?curid=857583" title="Valenciennellus">
<text>Valenciennellus is a genus of marine hatchetfishes. They are commonly known as constellationfishes.

==Species==
There are currently two recognized species in this genus:
* &quot;Valenciennellus carlsbergi&quot; 
* &quot;Valenciennellus tripunctulatus&quot; (Constellationfish)

Fossils of constellationfishes are known since the Early Eocene, more than 40 million years ago.

